column5: I was thinking about planning a guys weekend of fishing on bay of quinte  and spending the weekend in sleeper huts.  Can anyone recommend a good operator? Had some bad experiences with sleeper huts (terrible fishing).  thanks,  lovetofish
I don't believe there are any operators who offer this on Quinte
Quinte ice fishing team !  Call them no overnight cabins in Quinte that I know of ..
